  "Description": {
    "English": "The remains of a long-abandoned <span class=\"name name-stellar\">frigate</span>. Despite its ruined condition, it sails on through the stars...<br><br>Recruiting this vessel will add it to your frigate fleet. Manage your fleet from a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Fleet Command Room</span> aboard your freighter, and consult your <span class=\"name name-technology\">Navigator</span> to deploy frigates on lucrative expeditions.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘荒废已久的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">护卫舰</span>残骸。尽管严重受损，但是它仍然能够在群星之中航行......<br><br>招募这艘飞船将把它加入你的护卫舰舰队。在你货船上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">舰队指挥室</span>管理你的舰队，并咨询你的<span class=\"name name-technology\">领航员</span>在有利可图的探险中部署你的护卫舰。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "廢棄已久的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">巡防艦</span>殘骸。它雖破敗不堪，但仍在群星間航行......<br><br>招募這艘船，將其加到你的巡防艦艦隊。可在貨船上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">艦隊指揮處</span>管理艦隊，並向<span class=\"name name-technology\">領航員</span>諮詢巡防艦部署位置，開始探險賺錢。"
  },
